headline: If You Invested $10,000 In Kroger Stock 10 Years Ago, How Much Would You Have Now?
summary: Kroger Co. (NYSE:KR) is a food and drug retailer in the United States. The company operates combination food and drug stores, multi-department stores, marketplace stores and price-impact warehouses. It is set to report its Q4 2025 earnings on March 6, ...
